title: Jembaa Groove performs "Sweet My Ear" & more Live on KEXP

author: KEXP
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents Jembaa Groove performing live in the KEXP studio. Recorded October 3, 2025.

Songs:
Adesane 00:20
Sweet My Ear 04:40
Dabia 08:34
Namo 11:40
Amale 15:19

Eric Owusu - Vocals,Percussion
Yannick Nolting - Bass,Bandleader

Peter Somuah - Trumpet

Nir Sabag - Drums
